            <h2>Cancel the United Airlines Flights Ticket</h2>

            <p class="text-justify">Passengers on United Airlines can cancel a booked airline ticket directly through the company's website or by calling on the customer care number in the event of an emergency. You can use these <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/blog/united-airlines-flight-cancellation-policy.aspx">guidelines to cancel the flight tickets</a> correctly. First and foremost, you need to open your browser and go to United Airlines' official website. You must then go to the home page and click on the My Trips option. Then, in the appropriate field, type your booking confirmation code and last name. Finally, press the search tab to view your flight. After that, you must navigate to the flight you intend to cancel from the list, and then press the cancel button located next to the flight. Once this is completed, United will send you an email confirming the cancellation of your <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com">flight tickets</a>.</p>

            <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right-long"></i> United Airlines' Cancellation Policy: Learn it thoroughly</h3>

            <p class="text-justify">Passengers can use the <b>flight cancellation</b> service if certain limits and regulations are met. This Airline adheres to the usual 24-hour cancellation policy, which allows you to cancel a ticket for free in exchange for a full refund within the next 24 hours. You do, however, have the opportunity to cancel a ticket after 24 hours of booking for an additional fee. If you <b>cancel your ticket within 24 hours</b> but it departs before 7 days, you have to also pay a cancellation fee. This price ranges from $200 to $400 per ticket, and it is calculated according to ticket rate legislation. The refunds then start processing by the Airline using the passenger's original payment method. Non-refundable tickets, on the other hand, are processed as a credit to the passenger's future pocket. Furthermore, if you have any additional questions or issues about your reservations, you can contact a customer support representative immediately via phone. </p>

